State evolution follows

S(t+\Delta t)
=
S(t)
+
u(t)

The correction term depends on the four axes:

u(t) = Gate(I(t),E(t),\omega(t),C(t))

Therefore

S(t+\Delta t)
=
S(t)
+
Gate(I(t),E(t),\omega(t),C(t))


